Packages 
Package Description
bridge
Contains static reference points for high-level components.
mouseTools
Contains each of the different tools that are used to interact with the simulation.
planets
Everything relating to planets.
planets.physics
Everything related to the newtonian behavior of planets.
planets.physics.physicsObjects
Objects to be interacted with by the Physics Engine.
planets.render
Contains components directly involved with the rendering process.
planets.render.renderObjects
Relating to objects that need to be be rendered for the simulation.
projectData
All data that needs to be saved and loaded.
scheduler
In charge of scheduling tasks that need to be repeated regularly.
ui
Contains several UI elements to be applied to windows.
ui.drawer
Classes in charge of the drawers within the PropertiesPane.
unitConversion
Methods and conversion rates following the metric system.
unitTests
JUnit test cases for the project.
vector
Vector class and helpful vector math methods.
window
Window schema and WindowManager classes.
